casebody.data:
No. 129,

Orig.

Virginia v. Maryland. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 532 U. S. 969.]

Motion of the Special Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $181,228.28 for the period October 10, 2000, through July 31, 2001, to be paid equally by the parties.
